Oby Ezekwesili, the former minister of education and convener of BringBackourgirls campaign was on Tuesday harassed by security operatives at the presidential villa gate in Abuja. According to EIE Nigeria, they were harassed while protesting against recent killings. A video on the ‘Enough is Enough Nigeria’ official Twitter handle, shows the protesters being disrupted by security operatives. JUST IN
